- 'recent decade' refers to the years 2010 to 2019;
- The focus is on identifying artists based on their productivity within the specified period.

Earning a spot among the elite ten peaks refers to songs that are in the top 10 positions on the music chart;
Melodies are a metaphorical term used to refer to songs;
Climbed the highest is a metaphorical expression indicating reaching higher positions on the music chart.

sql:
SELECT chart_name
FROM charts
WHERE position <= 10;

SELECT position
FROM charts
ORDER BY position ASC;

SELECT AVG(spins) AS average_spins
FROM charts
WHERE chart_name = 'Billboard Hot 100';

SELECT total_tracks
FROM albums
WHERE album_name = "Thriller";

